

Nigeria needs more Bibles
          		 		  		
    
    
        
        
        
        
            
                
                    Persecuted Christians ravaged by Muslim
extremists need your help now more than ever.  View this email in
your browser.
                
                
                    A message from our ad partner:
                
                
                
                
                
                
                    
                    
                        
                            
                                
                            
                            
                                Thanks to the Challenge Grant,
just $4 provides two urgently needed Bibles to two persecuted
Christians uprooted by Muslim extremists.
                                SEND A BIBLE
                                
                            
                        
                    
                    Dear fellow Christ follower,
                    Since 2014, Islamic Extremists have carried
out 97 different attacks on Christians in Nigeria killing 2,781
and injuring men, women, and children.
                    And if you could see the heartrending
situation today in Nigeria with your own eyes, it would make you
sick.
                    Though the media doesn't cover it much, chaos
continues in the northern part of Nigeria, as Boko Haram attacks
Christians. Children are kidnapped as sex slaves, homes are
leveled, and parents are executed in front of their families.
                    But you can help today.
                    Many Nigerians have fled to live in camps,
leaving everything they own behind - including their Bibles. And
what's amazing is that because of a special $10,000 Challenge
Grant, your gift will be worth twice as much.
                    This means we could put a copy of God's Word
in the hands of 12,000 Nigerian Christians who have lost
everything and are desperate for hope!
                    A gift of $48 would normally send 12 Bibles.
But today, $48 will be doubled to $96, sending 24 Bibles. And a
generous gift of $96 now doubles to $192, sending 48 Bibles!
                    That's why I'm asking for your very best gift
to help place Bibles in their hands, knowing whatever you give
today will go twice as far thanks to the $10,000 Challenge Grant.
                    When you give, you'll be part of a more than
200-year legacy of sharing God's life-transforming Word through
Biblica - The International Bible Society.
                    So please give as generously as you can,
knowing your gift will put twice as many Bibles in the hands of
persecuted Christians desperate for the hope of God's Word.
                    Yours in Christ,
                    
                        
                            
                                
                                                                 
    	Dr. Carl A. Moeller
                                CEO, Biblica                     
                
                            
                        
                    
                    SEND A BIBLE
                    
                        
                            
                                
                                 
                                
                            
                        
                    
                    About Biblica
                    For over 200 years, Biblica has been
passionate about bringing the light of God's Word into the
darkest spiritual corners of the world. Click here to give
Bibles.

